			class="so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base"
			
		><h3 class="widget-title">Expert, Outsourced Contact Center Assistance from TeleDirect</h3>
<div class="siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget">
	<p>Industry-wide expertise for all of your call center needs – that’s the <a href="../index.php">TeleDirect</a> advantage. We’re already the industry leader for business process outsourcing (BPO) for <a href="../index.php">all types of industries</a>, including healthcare, insurance, and financial services.</p>
<p>If your business doesn’t fall into those “main” categories, no problem at all! With retail call center services, top-end education call center services and all solutions for call center technology companies, we have robust, ready-to-deploy products and services that will give you a decided advantage over the competition.</p>
<p><strong>TeleDirect: Call Center Services, and So Much More!</strong></p>
<p>Why do companies all across the globe choose TeleDirect? For one reason, our advance <a href="../index.php">call center platform</a> offers a flexible, affordable solution for any type of call center, regardless of industry. Plus, we have superior <a href="../../services/inbound/index.php">inbound </a>and <a href="../../services/outbound/index.php">outbound </a>client communication services, all of which help you tend to immediate client needs, even while growing your business.</p>
<p>Let’s look at three different industries where our call center services provide <a href="../../value-results/index.php">value and results</a>:</p>
<p><strong>Retail</strong>. Need retail call center help? TeleDirect offers a complete assortment of solutions, so you’ll stay on top of your business, and focus on what you do best! Thanks to our lead response management, our call center helps you gain additional retail clients, thanks to intuitive built-in marketing resources. Our retail call center platform is ready to take your business to the next level!</p>
<p><strong>Educational institutions</strong>. From tech schools to four-year universities, call centers are the “face” of your learning enterprise. It’s important to keep up with educational trends, and also ensure you’re meeting would-be client expectations. One area where we help with education call center services is with reservations. Face-to-face meetings are imperative for higher education establishments. Without this trust-building process, it’s impossible for students (and parents) to commit to your curriculum. With our <a href="../../services/inbound/reservation-services/index.php">reservation services</a>, TeleDirect locks in important meetings for financial assistance personnel, academic advisors, and more.</p>
<p><strong>Tech companie</strong>s. Many tech companies experience tremendous, unexpected growth – and that’s a good thing! But it can be tough on your client outreach strategy. Sudden business surges present challenges for even the most well-run contact centers. TeleDirect is used by technology companies everywhere for <a href="../../index.php">contact center assistance</a>. We let the engineers, software developers, and other personnel handle their core competencies, while we take care of customer calls, product bulletins, and anything else your company needs help with.</p>
<p><strong>Get the TeleDirect Advantage Today – For Any &amp; All Industries</strong></p>
<p>If you’re ready to take the next step and improve customer service, TeleDirect’s BPO call center system is ideal for retail call center, call centers for technology companies, and education call center services.</p>
<p>Just fill out our <a href="../../index.php#contact-form">customer contact form</a> to learn more. Our call center consultants are ready to help with your unique business process challenges. To speak directly with our staff, please call (800) 776-1081. Thanks for visiting TeleDirect!</p>
</div>
